latestPosts.caption:
a brand new personality 🎀💇🏻‍♀️✨

I always ask for nose-length curtain bangs and lots of face framing layers right under the curtain bangs!! make sure your hairstylist takes a bigger chunk of your hair for the curtain bangs as that creates more root/crown volume. and i ask her to give me a cut that ill have to style the least & would look great for an effortless blow out 💗 

* my hair type is STRAIGHT & thin. this cut probably won’t work for you if your hair type is different
